data.description:
This 2-bed, 2.5-bath townhouse is a charming and well-kept residence that combines modern features with comfort. The property includes a convenient 1-car garage, offering both security for your vehicle and additional storage space. One of the highlights of this townhouse is the screened patio, providing a perfect spot for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. This space allows you to enjoy the fresh air and scenic views while maintaining a comfortable and bug-free environment.
The newly renovated kitchen flooring adds a touch of contemporary elegance to the home. The townhouse's location is a key asset, being close to major interstates, shopping, and schools. 
Whether you are looking to relocate closer to your child's school, searching for your first home, or need to down-size, this is absolutely the perfect home for you! One more perk- The seller is offering a $1,500 credit with an acceptable offer.
